    "post_url": "https://t.me/ClashReport/78860",
    "text": "Even close Trump allies didn’t know what he would do. Multiple insiders believed he would reject the ceasefire offer — until he suddenly accepted it. Inside the Pentagon, officials were preparing for a massive bombing campaign. One defense official said: “We had no idea what was going to happen. It was wild.” Allies expected large-scale Iranian retaliation. Source: Axios",
